listing_company_name: Stone Real Estate - Tumbi Umbi and Berkeley Vale
description:
Ideally positioned within close proximity to all amenities, this four bedroom brick and tile home is overflowing with quality features and inclusions. The seamless floor plan provides functionality and harmony with huge welcoming living area, formal dining and family sized kitchen. All four bedrooms are of impressive size with built-in robes and main bedroom complete with ensuite. The features continue with an outdoor entertaining area perfect for enjoying that cup of tea, morning noon or night and entertaining area to amuse guests or watch the kids play in the generous 585sqm block (approx.). This home will tick all the boxes, don't be the one that misses out!

- Single level 4 bedroom brick home with a double lockup garage
- Sun drenched from front to back door with tones of street appeal
- Offering an oversized family living, with large kitchen + dining area
- All bedrooms with built in wardrobes and master complete with en-suite
- Rear outdoor entertaining area with low maintenance lawns
- Conveniently located just 5 minutes to Shelly beach, 2 minutes to local shops, 2 minutes from local schools and other amenities

View: By Appointment
Agency: Stone Real Estate
Agent: Luke Villata
